info: title: BrAPI version: '' openapi: 3.0.0 paths: {} components: schemas: SeedLotNewRequest: type: object properties: additionalInfo: additionalProperties: type: string description: Additional arbitrary info type: object seedLotName: description: A human readable name for this Seed Lot type: string example: Seed Lot Alpha seedLotDescription: description: A general description of this Seed Lot type: string example: This is a description of a seed lot sourceCollection: description: The description of the source where this material was originally collected (wild, nursery, etc) type: string example: nursery programDbId: description: The unique DbId of the breeding program this Seed Lot belongs to type: string example: e972d569 programName: description: The human readable name of the breeding program this Seed Lot belongs to type: string example: Tomatillo_Breeding_Program locationDbId: description: The unique identifier for a Location type: string example: 3cfdd67d locationName: description: A human readable name for a location type: string example: Location 1 storageLocation: description: Description the storage location type: string example: The storage location is an massive, underground, bunker. createdDate: description: The time stamp for when this seed lot was created type: string format: date-time lastUpdated: description: The timestamp for the last update to this Seed Lot (including transactions) type: string format: date-time contentMixture: description: |- The mixture of germplasm present in the seed lot.
If this seed lot only contains a single germplasm, the response should contain the name and DbId of that germplasm with a mixturePercentage value of 100
If the seed lot contains a mixture of different germplasm, the response should contain the name and DbId every germplasm present. The mixturePercentage field should contain the ratio of each germplasm in the total mixture. All of the mixturePercentage values in this array should sum to equal 100. type: array items: type: object properties: germplasmDbId: description: The unique DbId of the Germplasm contained in this Seed Lot type: string example: 029d705d germplasmName: description: The human readable name of the Germplasm contained in this Seed Lot type: string example: A0000003 crossDbId: description: The unique DbId for a cross contained in this seed lot type: string example: d105fd6f crossName: description: The human readable name for a cross contained in this seed lot type: string example: my_Crosses_2018_01 mixturePercentage: description: The percentage of the given germplasm in the seed lot mixture. type: integer example: 100 amount: description: Current balance of seeds in this lot. Could be a count (seeds, bulbs, etc) or a weight (kg of seed). type: number example: 561 units: description: Description of the things being counted in this Seed Lot (seeds, bulbs, kg, tree, etc) type: string example: seeds externalReferences: $ref: '#/components/schemas/ExternalReferences'
